{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"34b161a08b","title":"注意多打歼灭战少打击溃战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a2201a0ea","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"34b161a08b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"1b3b079386","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"3bc9e189c5","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":3,"text":"文，指文建武，当时任鄂豫陕军区司令员。汪，指汪锋，一九一○年生，陕西蓝田人，当时任鄂豫陕军区政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6a5e23d33c","type":"title","text":"注意多打歼灭战少打击溃战","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b"},{"id":"3bc9e189c5","type":"appellation","text":"文、汪：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b"},{"id":"a03a443ef1","type":"paragraph","text":"你们集中主力行动并已打了一个胜仗，甚慰。关于作战方法，请你们严重注意多打歼灭战，少打击溃战。打歼灭战的条件有二：（一）集中优势兵力包围敌军一部，每一仗只打一部分敌人，切不可同时打几部分敌人；（二）以主力打迂回，以一部打正面，切不可以一部打迂回，以主力打正面。你们如能实行上述两个条件，多打歼灭战，形势就会好转。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b"},{"id":"52d03463ab","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b"},{"id":"17232bebd1","type":"paragraph","text":"子漾","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b"}],"page":{"id":"b618a52ee2","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"34b161a08b","start":232,"end":232}}}},"__N_SSG":true}